" roman";="" color:#333333"=""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;line-height:15.75pt;background:white"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:ABeeZee;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333">1.&nbsp;Breakfast\r\nat 8:00am &gt; proceed to Agra via Yamuna Expressway.</span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:ABeeZee;mso-bidi-font-family:" times="" new="" roman";="" color:#333333"=""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;line-height:15.75pt;background:white"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:ABeeZee;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333">2.&nbsp;12:30 pm\r\nhotel check in &gt; have lunch&gt; 3:00 pm Taj Mahal visit</span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:ABeeZee;mso-bidi-font-family:" times="" new="" roman";="" color:#333333"=""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;line-height:15.75pt;background:white"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:ABeeZee;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333">3. &nbsp;5:00 pm\r\nshopping tours &gt; Back to hotel for dinner</span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:ABeeZee;mso-bidi-font-family:" times="" new="" roman";color:#333333"=""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:\r\n15.75pt;background:white"><b><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:ABeeZee;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333">Day 3:&nbsp;Agra-Jaipur (5 hours\r\ndrive)</span></b><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:ABeeZee;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n" times="" new="" roman";color:#333333"=""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;line-height:15.75pt;background:white"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:ABeeZee;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333">1.\r\n&nbsp;Breakfast at 8:00 am &gt; visit Agra fort.</span><span style="font-size:\r\n10.0pt;font-family:ABeeZee;mso-bidi-font-family:" times="" new="" roman";color:#333333"=""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;line-height:15.75pt;background:white"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:ABeeZee;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333">2. &nbsp;Jaipur\r\nenroute visiting FatehpurSikri (abandoned city of Mughal Empire)</span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:ABeeZee;mso-bidi-font-family:" times="" new="" roman";="" color:#333333"=""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:\r\n-18.0pt;line-height:15.75pt;background:white"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:ABeeZee;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333">3. &nbsp;Lunch at\r\nrestaurant</span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:ABeeZee;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\n" times="" new="" roman";color:#333333"=""><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:6.0pt;\r\nmargin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:\r\n15.75pt;background:white"><b><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:ABeeZee;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#333333">Day 4:&nbsp;Jaipur City Tour</span></b><