t></b></div><div><b><font size="3"><br></font></b></div><div><font size="3">After breakfast proceed to Colombo (Approximately 06 hours)-Colombo city is full of popular tourist attractions.</font></div><div><font size="3">National Museum - The National Museum of Colombo was established in 1877 by the British Governor Sir William Gregory which is the largest Museum in Sri Lanka. It has a good collection of historical work.</font></div><div><font size="3">Galle Face Green - South of Colombo along with the lined palm trees of Galle road is the Galle face Green. Along with the a greenish seafront you can enjoy the evening breeze and view the sun set.</font></div><div><font size="3"><br></font></div><div><font size="3"><b>DAY 04: &nbsp;COLOMBO - AIRPORT</b>&nbsp;</font></div><div><font size="3"><br></font></div><div><font size="3">After breakfast relax at the hotel</font></div><div><font size="3">Later proceed to airport for departure flight (Approximately 01 hour) - Please be at the airport 05 hours prior to flight departure.&nbsp;</font></div><div><br></div>', 'All Highway Toll fees,Hotel Accommodation at the above mentioned hotels on 01 DBL Room – BB basis,&nbsp;Hotels check in by 12:00 hrs. Check out by at 12:00 noon unless otherwise arranged,Hotels will be confirmed on availability at the time of booking. Alternatives will be suggested (if unavailable) prior to confirmation.', 'Airfare and Visa fee.(Online Visa application can be done at www.eta.gov.lk),Cost of Lunch &amp; Dinner throughout the tour,Expenses of personal nature,Any other service not specified above,Entrance fees &amp; joining fees for adventure tours and safari tours,Sightseeing places not included in the Tour Agenda,Meal costs other than included in the Hotel bookings,Driver tips,Transport -A/C CAR – USD 65 Per day,', '', '31 days or more before departure: 20% of the package cost,30 to 21 days before departure: 50% of the tour cost,20 days or less before departure: 100% of the package cost', '31 days or more before departure: 20% of the package cost,30 to 21 days before departure: 50% of the tour cost,20 days or less before departure: 100% of the package cost', '2017-03-21', '2017-12-20', NULL, '16.jpg-1490177369.jpg', '03.jpg-1490177369.jpg,,', 3, 67500, '2017-03-22 17:09:29', '2017-03-29 14:09:02'),
