ing SundaKelapa,old harbour and Fatahillah Museum, Glodok china town and &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; photostop at National Monument.<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Dinner will be served at local restaurant<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Transfer to the hotel.</font><br></li></ol><p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font size="3" face="arial"><b>Day 02: JakartaFull day Tour(B/L/D)</b></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"></p><ol><li><font size="3">Breakfast at the hotel.<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Afterward visit Beautiful Indonesia in Miniature Park, followed by shopping at ITC ManggaDua or Tanah Abang Mall.<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Lunch &amp; Dinner at local restaurant.</font></li></ol><p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font size="3" face="arial"><b>Day 03: Jakarta - Puncak– Bandung</b></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"></p><ol><li><font size="3">Breakfast at the hotel<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Afterward direct transfer to Puncak.<br></font></li><li><font size="3">On the way visit Safari wild life Park &amp;Puncak Tea plantation.<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Then straight to Bandung.<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Lunch &amp; dinner at local restaurant.<br></font></li><li><font size="3">In the evening check in Hotel at Bandung</font></li></ol><p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font size="3" face="arial"><b>Day 04: Bandung Full Day</b></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"></p><ol><li><font size="3">Breakfast at the hotel.<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Full day Bandung Tour:visiting White Crater volcano and RancaUpashotspring + Ciwidey strawberry farm.<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Lunch at local restaurant.<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Then back to Bandung &nbsp;andshop at Factory Outlet such as Rumah Mode, Heritage, The Summit and The Kosmo or &nbsp; Cihampelas.<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Dinner at local restaurant &nbsp;then free program.</font></li></ol><p></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font size="3" face="arial"><b>Day 05: Transfer(Bandung/Jakarta)</b></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"></p><ol><li>Breakfast at the hotel.<br></li><li>Free time until transfer to Bandung/Jakarta airport for next flight<br></li></ol><p></p>', 'Return Air ticket (Dhaka- Jakarta) by Air, Private\r\nair-conditioned transportation, \r\n\r\nAccommodation\r\nat Hotel 88 Jakarta, \r\n\r\nGuide\r\nservice,\r\n\r\n&nbsp;Admission &amp;parking fees,\r\n\r\nDonations, \r\n\r\nToll road\r\nMeals per itinerary,', 'Meals (other than mentioned in the program),Drinks,Mineral water beyond that supplied,Tips,Early check in or late check out,Insurances,Optional excursions and activities,Additional transfer required due to any emergency situation,Items of a personal nature (Phone calls, laundry, beverages…),Peak season surcharges if any,All not mentioned above', '', '31 days or more before departure: 20% of the package cost,30 to 21 days before departure: 50% of the tour cost,20 days or less before departure: 100% of the package cost', '31 days or more before departure: 20% of the package cost,30 to 21 days before departure: 50% of the tour cost,20 days or less before departure: 100% of the package cost', '2017-05-01', '2017-12-20', NULL, 'Jkarta_4.jpg-1490187720.jpg', 'Jkarta_3.jpg-1490187720.jpg,Jkarta_2.jpg-1490187720.jpg,Jkarta_5.jpg-1490187720.jpg', 3, 41999, '2017-03-22 08:02:00', '2017-04-05 08:11:00'),
