ificent acropolis of Pergamum.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="arial" size="3">&nbsp; &nbsp;3. Dinner.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="arial" size="3">&nbsp; &nbsp;4. Overnight Kusadasi &nbsp;hotel.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium;">Day 03: Ephesus, Kusadasi (B, D)</b><br></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium;">&nbsp; &nbsp;1. Breakfast at hotel.</span><br></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="arial" size="3">&nbsp; &nbsp;2. History day with a guided tour of Ephesus and a visit to the site of the Temple of Artemis.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="arial" size="3">&nbsp; &nbsp;3. Visit Greek village of Sirince, famous for its fruit wines, Carpet weaving carpet village.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="arial" size="3">&nbsp; &nbsp;4. Dinner at hotel.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="arial" size="3">&nbsp; &nbsp;5. Overnight Kusadasi.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium;">Day 04: Pamukkale, Hierapolis(B, D)</b><br></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium;">&nbsp; &nbsp;1. Breakfast at hotel.</span><br></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="arial" size="3">&nbsp; &nbsp;2. This morning enjoy a display of locally handcrafted leather goods before heading to the magnificent white calcium terraces, known as Travertines, in Pamukkale, tour to the ancient city of Hierapolis.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="arial" size="3">&nbsp; &nbsp;3. Dinner at hotel.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="arial" size="3">&nbsp; &nbsp;4. Overnight Pamukkale &nbsp;hotel.</font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium;">Day 05: &nbsp;Marmaris (B)</b><br></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium;">&nbsp; &nbsp;1. Breakfast at hotel.</span><br></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="arial" size="3">&nbsp; &nbsp;2. After breakfast transferred to Marmaris airport.</font></p>', '&nbsp;Return Air ticket (Dhaka-Istanbul-Dhaka) with applicable all taxes, &nbsp;Accommodation in twin/double room with daily breakfast, &nbsp;All transfers and transportation (types of vehicles depending on the number of pax),Meals (B/L/D) (Breakfast/Lunch/Dinner) as indicated in the program (Halal food)', 'Meals (other than mentioned in the program),Drinks,Visas to Turkey,Tips,Early check in or late check out,Insurances,Optional excursions and activities,Additional transfer required due to any emergency situation,Items of a personal nature (Phone calls, laundry, beverages…),Peak season surcharges if any,All not mentioned above.', '', '31 days or more before departure: 20% of the package cost,30 to 21 days before departure: 50% of the tour cost,20 days or less before departure: 100% of the package cost', '31 days or more before departure: 20% of the package cost,30 to 21 days before departure: 50% of the tour cost,20 days or less before departure: 100% of the package cost', '2017-05-01', '2017-12-20', NULL, 'Turkish_5.jpg-1490190287.jpg', 'Turkish_6.jpg-1490190287.jpg,Turkish_7.jpg-1490190287.jpg,Turkish_8.jpg-1490190287.jpg', 3, 131000, '2017-03-22 08:44:47', '2017-04-05 11:32:09');
