(97, 5, 1, 0, 'BELLISSIMA BALI!!', 'INDONESIA', 'BALI', 'TSL', 1, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, NULL, '3 Days / 2 Nights', NULL, '<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><font face="arial" size="3">Bali is an Indonesian island known for its forested volcanic mountains, iconic rice paddies, beaches and coral reefs. The island is home to religious sites such as cliffside Uluwatu Temple. To the south, the beachside city of Kuta has lively bars, while Seminyak, Sanur and Nusa Dua are popular resort towns. The island is also known for its yoga and meditation retreats.(Source: Wikipedia)</font></span></div>', '<div><font size="3"><b>Day 01: Arrival Bali – (D)</b></font></div><div><span style="font-size: medium;"><br></span></div><div><ol><li><font size="3">Arrive at Bali Airport.<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Meet and greet at airport<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Transfer to the hotel.<br></font></li><li><font size="3">In the evening at 6PM pick up at hotel lobby and proceed to dinner at Indian Restaurant.</font></li></ol></div><div><font size="3"><b><br></b></font></div><div><font size="3"><b>Day 02: &nbsp;Full dayUbud Monkey Forest + &nbsp;Kintamani tour (B/L/D)</b></font></div><div><br></div><div><ol><li><font size="3">Breakfast &nbsp;at hotel<br></font></li><li><font size="3">At 10AMpick up at lobby hotel then proceed to Fullday tour: Ubud Monkey forest + Kintamani tour ( 8 Hours ).<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Enroute stops at Ubud Monkey Forest, coffee and cacao plantation at Madu Pertiwi Agro Tourism<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Lunch at local restaurant in Kintamani area ( buffet style )<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Dinner at Indian Restaurant<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Return &nbsp;to the hotel.<br></font></li></ol></div><div><br></div><div><font size="3"><b>Day 03: Full day Glass Bottom Boat Tj. Benoa+Tanah Lot Sunset tour(B/L/D)</b></font></div><div><font size="3"><br></font></div><div><ol><li><font size="3">Breakfast<br></font></li><li><font size="3">At 10.00AM, pick up at lobby hotel and proceed to Tj. Benoa to take Glass Bottom boat Turtle Island. Water sport activities : banana boat , parasailing , seawalker and etc ( Water Sport On Personal Expenses )<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Lunch will at Indian Restaurant.<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Then continue to Tanah Lot Sunset tour.<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Dinner at Indian Restaurant<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Return to the hotel.</font><br></li></ol></div><div><b><br></b></div><div><font size="3"><b>Day 04: 2 Hours HerritageSpa &nbsp;- &nbsp;Tanah Lot Sunset tour (B/D)</b></font></div><div><font size="3"><b><br></b></font></div><div><ol><li><font size="3">Breakfast<br></font></li><li><font size="3">At 11.30 AM picked up to have lunch at Local Restaurant<br></font></li><li><font size="3">After lunch 2 hours Spa at Spa Center.<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Then visit Tanah Lot temple<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Return to hotel and free at own leisure.</font></li></ol></div><div><font size="3"><b>&nbsp;</b></font></div><div><font size="3"><b>Day 05 :Transfer out &nbsp; &nbsp;(B)</b></font></div><div><font size="3"><b><br></b></font></div><div><ol><li><font size="3">Breakfast at hotel.<br></font></li><li><font size="3">Pick up at hotel lobby.<br></font></li><li><font size="3">See off at airport for departure flight.</font><br></li></ol></div>', 'Return Air ticket (Dhaka-Denpasar(Bali)-Dhaka) with all applicable taxes ,2 nights comfortable stay at Wina Holiday Homes or similar 3*standard Hotel,Accommodation Twin share basis,Complimentary Breakfast,Free Wi-Fi Internet,Free Transfers', 'Meals (other than mentioned in the program),Drinks,Tips,Early check in or late check out,Insurances,Optional excursions and activities,Additional transfer required due to any emergency situation,Items of a personal nature (Phone calls, laundry, beverages…),Peak season surcharges if any,All not mentioned above.