p;Sodium| Potassium | Calcium | Urine Routine | Stool Routine | TSH | PSA / PAP Smear | ECG | Tread Mill Stress Test | PFT (Lung Function Test) | &nbsp;X-ray Chest PA View | &nbsp;USG Whole Abdomen (Screening) | Physician Consultation | Dental Consultation.', 'Advance purchase only', 'Medical packages once sold and confirmed is not refundable or exchangeable with other offers,Medical packages once sold and confirmed&nbsp;cannot be Transferable to other passengers.', '2017-03-23', '2017-10-31', NULL, 'screenshot.jpg-1490425287.jpg', 'hcp-s2.jpg-1490425287.jpg,,', 3, 22999, '2017-03-23 11:34:11', '2017-04-05 08:39:57');
