font></div><div><font size="3">1. On arrival in Singapore, check- in at the hotel and spend the day at leisure.</font></div><div><font size="3">2. In the evening, proceed for Singapore Night Safari Tour.</font></div><div><font size="3">3. Visit the nocturnal zoo and see the many animals in their full splendor.</font></div><div><font size="3">4. A tram ride is also offered for those who do not wish to walk. Later, return to the hotel for overnight stay.</font></div><div><font size="3"><b><br></b></font></div><div><font size="3"><b>Day 02: Singapore - City Highlights and Afternoon Sentosa:</b></font></div><div><font size="3">1. After breakfast, enjoy a 2-hour tour of the city.</font></div><div><font size="3">2. In the afternoon, head to Sentosa Island for the Sentosa Underwater Tour.</font></div><div><font size="3">3. Visit the Merlion and view the underwater world.</font></div><div><font size="3">4. Enjoy your experience on the Luge and witness a beautiful sound and light show - Songs of the Sea.</font></div><div><font size="3">5. Return to the hotel for an overnight stay.</font></div><div><font size="3"><br></font></div><div><font size="3"><b>Day 03: Leisure Day at Hotel / Optional Tour:</b></font></div><div><font size="3">1. After breakfast, spend the day exploring the city at your leisure.</font></div><div><font size="3">2. Stay overnight at the hotel.</font></div><div><font size="3"><br></font></div><div><font size="3"><b>Day 04: Departure from Singapore:</b></font></div><div><font size="3">1. After breakfast, spend some time at leisure.</font></div><div><font size="3">2. Check out from the hotel and transfer to the airport for your return journey.</font></div>', 'Air fare: Round Trip (Dhaka-Singapore) ,2 Nights’ Accommodation with breakfast,Return Airport Transfers by SIC basis,Half day City Tour with English speaking guide on SIC basis,Night Safari on SIC basis,Sunset Sentosa (1 way cable car, SEA Aquarium and Wings of Time)on SIC basis, For 5 Star hotels complimentary upgrade to PVT Airport Transfers and Tours by SIC basis,The above rate quoted in SGD Dollars,per person.', 'Camera fee, Alcoholic / Non- Alcoholic beverages, Travel insurance, Any Airfare / Train fare, Expenses caused by factors beyond our control like rail and flight delays.', '', '31\r\ndays or more before departure: 20% of the package cost,30\r\nto 21 days before departure: 50% of the tour cost,20\r\ndays or less before departure: 100% of the package cost', '&nbsp;31\r\ndays or more before departure: 20% of the package cost,30\r\nto 21 days before departure: 50% of the tour cost,20\r\ndays or less before departure: 100% of the package cost', '2017-05-01', '2017-12-20', NULL, 'Singapore_4.jpg-1490426564.jpg', 'Singapore_1.jpg-1490426564.jpg,Singapore_2.jpg-1490426564.jpg,Singapore_3.jpg-1490426564.jpg', 3, 52000, '2017-03-25 14:22:44', '2017-03-29 14:13:01'),
