sp;</font></div><div><font size="3">1. On arrival at the airport, head to the hotel. Check in and take rest for a little.</font></div><div><font size="3">2. After that go on a city tour in Singapore.</font></div><div><font size="3">3. Visit Chinatown, Marina Bay and Little India.</font></div><div><font size="3">4. Enjoy the cable car ride from Mt. Faber. Relax till evening &amp; proceed for Night Safari.</font></div><div><font size="3"><br></font></div><div><font size="3">Day 02:</font></div><div><font size="3">1. In the afternoon after lunch, enjoy your day at Sentosa Island.</font></div><div><font size="3">2. Take an amazing cable car ride to reach Sentosa.</font></div><div><font size="3">3. Explore the marine realm of S.E.A. Aquarium, home to more than 100,000 marine animals of over 800 species. Songs of the Sea or Wings of Time brings you a mesmerizing show with a live cast, dramatic effects and pyrotechnics.</font></div>', '2 Nights’ Accommodation with breakfast,Airfare: Round Trip (Dhaka-Singapore-Dhaka), Return Airport Transfers by SIC basis, Half day City Tour with English speaking guide on SIC basis, Night Safari on SIC basis,Sunset Sentosa (1 way cable car, SEA Aquarium and Wings of Time) on SIC basis, &nbsp;For 5 Star hotels complimentary upgrade to PVT Airport Transfers and Tours by SIC basis, The above rate quoted in SGD Dollars, per person.', 'Camera fee,Alcoholic / Non- Alcoholic beverages,Travel insurance, Any Airfare / Train fare, Expenses caused by factors beyond our control like rail and flight delays.', '', '31 days or more before departure: 20% of the package\r\ncost,30 to 21 days before departure: 50% of the tour\r\ncost,20 days or less before departure: 100% of the\r\npackage cost', '31 days or more before departure: 20% of the package cost,30 to 21 days before departure: 50% of the tour cost,20 days or less before departure: 100% of the package cos', '2017-05-01', '2017-12-20', NULL, 'Singpore_Chinatown.jpg-1490428753.jpg', 'Singapore_MarinaBay1.jpg-1490428753.jpg,Singapore_MarinaBay2.jpg-1490428753.jpg,Singapore_acquiram1.jpg-1490428753.jpg', 3, 43000, '2017-03-25 14:59:13', '2017-04-05 08:06:26');
