(111, 1, 0, 0, 'BLEND WITH BALINESE', 'INDONESIA', 'BALI', 'TSL', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, '4 DAYS / 3 NIGHTS', NULL, '<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Lato, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15.0396px;" class="cye-lm-tag">Bali is an Indonesian island known for its forested volcanic mountains, iconic rice paddies, beaches and coral reefs. The island is home to religious sites such as cliffside Uluwatu Temple. To the south, the beachside city of Kuta has lively bars, while Seminyak, Sanur and Nusa Dua are popular resort towns. The island is also known for its yoga and meditation retreats.</span><br>', '<h4><font size="4"><font face="arial"><b>Day 1: &nbsp;Arrival at Bali (D)</b></font><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="arial">1. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Arrival at Bali Airport.</font><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="arial">2. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Meet and greet and transfer to the hotel.</font><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="arial">3. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; In the evening at 6 PM pick up at hotel lobby and proceed to dinner at Indian &nbsp;Restaurant.</font><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="arial"><b><br></b></font></font></h4><h4><font size="4"><font face="arial"><b>Day 2: &nbsp;Fullday Ubud Monkey Forest + &nbsp;Kintamani tour (B/L/D )</b></font><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="arial">1. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; After breakfast at 10AM, &nbsp; pick up at lobby hotel then proceed to Fullday Ubud Monkey forest + Kintamani tour ( 8 Hours ). &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Enroute stops at Ubud Monkey Forest, the holy spring of Tirta Empul at Tampak Siring, coffee and cacao plantation at Madu &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Pertiwi Agro Tourism.</font></font></h4><h4>2. &nbsp; Lunch will provide at local restaurant in Kintamani area ( buffet style )<font size="4"><font face="arial"><br></font></font></h4><h4><font size="4"><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="arial">3. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Dinner will be provided at Indian Restaurant ,</font><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="arial">4. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; then get back to the hotel.</font><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="arial">&nbsp;</font><font face="arial"><br></font><b><font face="arial">Day 3: &nbsp;Fullday Glass Bottom Boat Tj. Benoa + &nbsp;Tanah Lot Sunset tour(B/L/D )</font><font face="arial"><br></font></b><font face="arial">1. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; After breakfast at 10.00AM,</font><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="arial">2. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; pick up at lobby hotel and proceed to Tj. Benoa to take Glass Bottom boat Turtle Island.</font><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="arial">3. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;You will enjoy water sport activities like banana boat , parasailing , seawalker and etc ( Water Sport On Personal Expenses )</font><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="arial">4. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Lunch will be provided at Indian Restaurant.</font><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="arial">5. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Then continue to Tanah Lot Sunset tour</font><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="arial">6. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Dinner will be provided at Indian Restaurant then back to the hotel</font><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="arial">&nbsp;</font><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="arial"><b>Day 4: &nbsp;Transfer out(B)</b></font><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="arial">1. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Breakfast at hotel.</font><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="arial">2. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Pick up at hotel lobby</font><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="arial">3. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Drop at airport for departure flight</font></font></h4><h5><br></h5>', '&nbsp;Return Air Ticket ( Dhaka-Bali-Dhaka) ,3Nights Accommodation at Hotel , Daily Breakfast Lunch and Dinner at as per Itinerary, &nbsp; Return transfers All program as itinerary, &nbsp;English Speaking Guide Based on the lowest room category', '', '', '', '', '2017-03-25', '2017-12-20', NULL, 'sunset-bali.jpg-1490452746.jpg', '011KudeTaBeach.jpg-1490452746.jpg,wina-holiday-villa-hotel.jpg-1490452746.jpg,wina-holiday-villa-hotel (1).jpg-1490452746.jpg', 4, 44999, '2017-03-25 09:39:06', '2017-04-05 18:34:17'),
