(114, 1, 0, 0, 'SINFULL BY PATTAYA', 'THAILAND', 'PATTAYA', 'TSL', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, '5days/4Nights', NULL, '<p style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:11.25pt;margin-left:\r\n0in;background:whitesmoke"><span style="font-size:11.5pt;font-family:" segoe="" ui="" light","sans-serif";="" mso-bidi-font-family:arial;color:black"="">Return Air ticket (Dhaka-Bangkok-Dhaka)\r\nwith all applicable taxes by US-Bangla Airlines, 4 nights comfortable stay\r\nat&nbsp;3*standard Hotel in Bangkok &amp; Pattaya, Accommodation is based on Twin sharing basis, Complimentary Breakfast,\r\nFree Wi-Fi Internet<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p style="padding: 0px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><font size="3" face="arial">Day 1:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (-/-/-)</font></strong></p><ul style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 25px; padding: 0px;"><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 20px;"><font size="3" face="arial">Meet and greet at Suvarnabhumi International Airport</font></li><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 20px;"><font size="3" face="arial">Check in at Pattaya Hotel</font></li><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 20px;"><font size="3" face="arial">Free at leisure</font></li><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 20px;"><font size="3" face="arial">Overnight stay at Pattaya Hotel</font></li></ul><p style="padding: 0px;"><font size="3" face="arial">&nbsp;</font></p><p style="padding: 0px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><font size="3" face="arial">Day 2:&nbsp;</font></strong></p><ul style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 25px; padding: 0px;"><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 20px;"><font size="3" face="arial">Breakfast at Hotel Restaurant</font></li><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 20px;"><font size="3" face="arial">Free at leisure</font></li><li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;