<span style="color: rgb(23, 44, 52);" class="cye-lm-tag"><font face="arial" size="3">Tanah Lot, simple in its construction, is dramatic in its\r\nocean-front location and is<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span style="color: rgb(23, 44, 52);" class="cye-lm-tag"><font face="arial" size="3">one of the main temples in the worship of Balinese Gods. Dinner\r\nwill be provided<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="text-align:justify"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: rgb(23, 44, 52);" class="cye-lm-tag"><font face="arial" size="3">at Indian Restaurant then back to the hotel .</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><font face="arial" size="3"><b><font color="#000000">Day 4</font><span style="color: rgb(255, 78, 4);" class="cye-lm-tag"> </span></b><b>Fullday Glass Bottom\r\nBoat Tj. Benoa </b>+ <b>Uluwatu Temple tour\r\n(B/L/D)</b><o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span style="color: rgb(23, 44, 52);" class="cye-lm-tag"><font face="arial" size="3">After Breakfast at 10.00AM, pick up at lobby hotel and proceed\r\nto Tj. Benoa to take<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span style="color: rgb(23, 44, 52);" class="cye-lm-tag"><font face="arial" size="3">Glass Bottom boat Turtle Island. You will enjoy water sport\r\nactivities like banana<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="M