\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span style="color: rgb(23, 44, 52);" class="cye-lm-tag"><font face="arial" size="3">on a relaxing cruise around the harbour. Take in the cool night\r\nair on the top desk,<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span style="color: rgb(23, 44, 52);" class="cye-lm-tag"><font face="arial" size="3">be entertained by our live musical entertainers at the bridge\r\ndeck, savour a<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span style="color: rgb(23, 44, 52);" class="cye-lm-tag"><font face="arial" size="3">delicious international buffet dinner, then dance the night away\r\nat our disco or<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="text-align:justify"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: rgb(23, 44, 52);" class="cye-lm-tag"><font face="arial" size="3">enjoy our live cabaret show.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><font face="arial" size="3"><b><font color="#000000">Day 6</font><span style="color: rgb(255, 78, 4);" class="cye-lm-tag"> </span></b><b>Transfer out (B)</b><span style="color: rgb(23, 44, 52);" class="cye-lm-tag"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\nnormal;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none"><span style="color: rgb(23, 44, 52);" class="cye-lm-tag"><font face="arial" size="3">Breakfast at hotel. Pick up at lobby hotel will be arranged 3\r\nhours before departure<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag"><span style="line-height: 115%; color: rgb(23, 44, 52);" class="cye-lm-tag"><font face="arial" size="3">flight,\r\ntransfer out to Bali Airport.</font></span><o:p></o:p></p>', 'Return Air Ticket ( Dhaka-Bali) ,5 Night accommodation at 4star Hotel,Daily Breakfast,Lunch and Dinner as per Itinerary,Return transfers,All program as itinerary,English Speaking Guide,Based on the lowest category room', '', '', '', '', '2017-03-01', '2017-12-31', NULL, '01.jpg-1490459239.jpg', 'bali-tours6.jpg-1490459240.jpg,Best Western.jpg-1490459240.jpg,Hotel Room.jpg-1490459240.jpg', 3, 58999, '2017-03-25 11:27:19', '2017-04-05 18:35:14'),
(125, 1, 0, 0, 'BEST OF KASHMIR', 'INDIA', 'SRINAGAR | Pahalgam | Gulmarg | Sonmarg | Nishatbagh & Shalimar Bagh', 'TSL', 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, NULL, '6 Days 5 Nights', NULL, '<p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family: " century="" gothic",="" sans-serif;="" background-image:="" initial;="" background-position:="" background-size:="" background-repeat:="" background-attachment:="" background-origin:="" background-clip:="" initial;"="" class="cye-lm-tag">Kashmir is the northwestern region\r\nof the Indian subcontinent. Kashmir reminded as another name for paradise throughout\r\nthe ages; framed in the lap of majestic mountains of the Himalayas. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family: " century="" gothic",="" sans-serif;="" background-image:="" initial;="" background-position:="" background-size:="" background-repeat:="" background-attachment:="" background-origin:="" background-clip:="" initial;"="" class="cye-lm-tag">Rimmed by layers of alpine peaks,\r\nthe 140km-long Kashmir Valley opens up as a giant, flat upland bowl of lakes and\r\norchards. Tin-roofed villages guard terraced paddy fields delineated by apple\r\ngroves and pin-straight poplars. Proudly independent-minded Kashmiris mostly\r\nfollow a Sufi-based Islamic faith, worshipping in distinctive box-shaped\r\nmosques with central spires. The region is also known for its Amarnathji Yatra.</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="text-align:justify">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="text-align:right" align="right"><span style="font-family: " century="" gothic",="" sans-serif;="" background-image:="" initial;="" background-position:="" background-size:="" background-repeat:="" background-attachment:="" background-origin:="" background-clip:="" initial;"="" class="cye-lm-tag">Source:\r\nlonely planet.</span><b><span style="font-family:" century="" gothic","sans-serif""="" class="cye-lm-tag"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>', '<p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag"><font size="4" face="arial"><b style="text-align: justify;"><span times="" new="" roman";color:black"="" class="cye-lm-tag">Route plan&nbsp;</span></b><b style="text-align: justify;"><span times="" new="" roman";color:black"="" class="cye-lm-tag">Itinerary</span></b><br></font></p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nbackground:white"><span times="" new="" roman";color:black"="" class="cye-lm-tag"><font size="4" face="arial">One day kolkata for free eye check up with hotel\r\nfacilities,<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nbackground:white"><span times="" new="" roman";color:black"="" class="cye-lm-tag"><font size="4" face="arial">Route plan: Dhaka- Kolkata (<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nnormal">1 night stop over</b>) –Srinagar-same return route<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nbackground:white"><span times="" new="" roman";color:black"="" class="cye-lm-tag"><font size="4" face="arial">Free eye check up with free appointed\r\nhospital/doctor @ Kolkata or enjoy free time.&nbsp;</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nbackground:white"><span times="" new="" roman";color:black"="" class="cye-lm-tag"><font size="4" face="arial"><br></font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;background:white"><b style="font-family: arial; font-size: large;"><span times="" new="" roman";color:#333333"="" class="cye-lm-tag">Day 01: Kolkata &gt;\r\nSrinagar</span></b><br></p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;background:white"><span times="" new="" roman";color:#333333"="" class="cye-lm-tag"><font size="4" face="arial">On arrival at\r\nSrinagar, you will be met by our representative at the airport and will be\r\ntransferred&nbsp; to Deluxe Houseboat.&nbsp; Afternoon Shikara ride on the Dal\r\nLake to enjoy the beauty that God has graced this city with which is often\r\ncompared to Venice. You will get a view of some very interesting places around\r\nthe lake.&nbsp; Overnight stay at Houseboat.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;background:white"><font size="4" face="arial"><b><span times="" new="" roman";color:#333333"="" class="cye-lm-tag">Day 02: Pahalgam</span></b><span times="" new="" roman";="" color:#333333"="" class="cye-lm-tag"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;background:white"><span times="" new="" roman";color:#333333"="" class="cye-lm-tag"><font size="4" face="arial">Full day\r\nexcursion to Pahalgam 2440 Mtrs (vale of Kashmir) on the way visit Saffron\r\nfields, Avantipur ruins and Anantnagsulpher spring. Pahalgam is the most famous\r\nplace for Indian Film Industry. Enjoy the nature charm of the valley. In the\r\nevening return back to Houseboat.&nbsp;&nbsp; Overnight at Houseboat.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;background:white"><font size="4" face="arial"><b><span times="" new="" roman";color:#333333"="" class="cye-lm-tag">Day 03: Gulmarg</span></b><span times="" new="" roman";="" color:#333333"="" class="cye-lm-tag"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;background:white"><span times="" new="" roman";color:#333333"="" class="cye-lm-tag"><font size="4" face="arial">Full day tour of\r\nGulmarg which is one of the most beautiful summer resorts in the valley. It is\r\nalso&nbsp;&nbsp; popular &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;for its&nbsp;&nbsp; golf\r\ncourse&nbsp;&nbsp; (in summer), the highest in the world&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\nand&nbsp;&nbsp; skiing during the winter season. Enjoy the splendor of nature\r\nand the snowy mountains. One can have Gondola ride (cable car) from Gulmarg to\r\nKhalinmarg In the evening return to Houseboat.&nbsp; Overnight at Houseboat.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;background:white"><font size="4" face="arial"><b><span times="" new="" roman";color:#333333"="" class="cye-lm-tag">Day 04: Sonmarg</span></b><span times="" new="" roman";="" color:#333333"="" class="cye-lm-tag"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;background:white"><span times="" new="" roman";color:#333333"="" class="cye-lm-tag"><font size="4" face="arial">Full day\r\nexcursion to Sonmarg which is the most beautiful drive from Srinagar. On the\r\nway we stop at many beautiful spots. Continue drive to Sonmarg 2690 Mtrs\r\n(Meadow of Gold). One can ride on horse to visit to Thajiwas Glacier where snow\r\nremains round the year and Sonmarg is known as Gateway of Ladakh. In the\r\nevening return to Houseboat. Overnight at Houseboat/Hotel<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;background:white"><font size="4" face="arial"><b><span times="" new="" roman";color:#333333"="" class="cye-lm-tag">Day 05: Nishatbagh\r\n&amp; Shalimar Bagh</span></b><span times="" new="" roman";color:#333333"="" class="cye-lm-tag"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;background:white"><span times="" new="" roman";color:#333333"="" class="cye-lm-tag"><font size="4" face="arial">Day tour of world\r\nfamous Mughal Gardens visiting the NishatBagh (The garden of pleasure) and\r\nShalimar Bagh (Abode of love), Chesh Ma Shahi (Royal Spring garden) and\r\nShankracharya temple where from you will have the fantastic view of the whole\r\nSrinagar city and lakes. In the evening return back.&nbsp; Overnight at\r\nHouseboat/Hotel<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;background:white"><font size="4" face="arial"><b><span times="" new="" roman";color:#333333"="" class="cye-lm-tag">Day 06: Onward\r\nDestination Flight</span></b><span times="" new="" roman";color:#333333"="" class="cye-lm-tag"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag" style="margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;background:white"><span times="" new="" roman";color:#333333"="" class="cye-lm-tag"><font size="4" face="arial">Transfer in time\r\nto the airport to connect onwards destination flight.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal cye-lm-tag">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n  <o:AllowPNG/>\r\n </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n</xml><![endif]-->\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:TrackMoves/>\r\n  <w:TrackFormatting/>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:DoNotPromoteQF/>\r\n  <w:LidThemeOther>EN-US</w:LidThemeOther>\r\n  <w:LidThemeAsian>JA</w:LidThemeAsian>\r\n  <w:LidThemeComplexScript>X-NONE</w:LidThemeComplexScript>\r\n  <w:Compatibility>\r\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>\r\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>\r\n   <w:WrapTextWit